  exact ‚ü®œÜ.hom‚ÇÉ, S.W.comp_mem _ _ (W.mk S H.mem mem‚ÇÑ') (W.mk' S H'.mem mem‚ÇÖ'),
    by simpa [œÜ] using œÜ.comm‚ÇÇ, by simpa [œÜ] using œÜ.comm‚ÇÉ‚ü©‚ü©

